      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, though a discerning eye might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every button, dial, and screen functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict maintenance schedule with recent service records for the brakes and fluids available for review. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and offers a firm, responsive ride. This is a reliable, attractive car ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
